[section "The Aptixia Client Library"]
The Aptixia Client Library provides client side access to an aptixia
test server. 

[section "Connecting to a test server"]

[section {Managed vs Unmanaged data}]
[subsection {Managed Data Types}]
    TBD
[subsection {Unmanaged Data Types}]
    Unmanaged data types are used for conveying input, output, 
    and input/output, parameter data in Object method calls.

[section {Objects}]
    Objects are Managed. They reflect Objects resident within the
    TestServer.

[section "Object Methods"]
    [subsection "Method Calls on subobjects"]

[section "Object Properties"]
    Objects properties, being intrinsic elements in Objects, are Managed data

[section "Simple Object Properties"]
